snippet.title: Norrland Trailer
snippet.description:
A game made for an art exhibition at Kulturbygden in Sollefteå. The theme was "Kärlek i Norrland" (love up north). I printed ten copies of the game, and will sell these on my site. Once they're all sold, the game will be put online for anyone to play for free.

http://blog.cactusquid.com/
